{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_greyy_set_1", "eventName": "過濾星星", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "過濾星星", "storyInfo": "橫遭突變的男孩，心中仍舊懷著父母的教誨。在被救起之後，他決定用自己的方式表達感謝。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿上東西，是貧民區那邊！", "name": "辦事處幹員A"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到晚上才拿到消息，我們已經遲了，看看還能不能做點什麼......把醫療設備都準備好，我們要在這裡——", "name": "辦事處幹員A"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——不能在這裡，現在還不確定到底發生了什麼，穩妥起見我們不能太招搖。", "name": "辦事處幹員B"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的對......把醫療帳篷拿出來吧，山後樹林從來都沒人去，在那裡搭。我們去貧民區一趟！", "name": "辦事處幹員A"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡！", "name": "辦事處幹員A"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，孩子，醒醒？能聽見我們說話嗎？", "name": "辦事處幹員B"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身上沒有源石結晶，看不出來是不是感染者......他抱了個什麼，一根法杖嗎？這麼小的孩子......", "name": "辦事處幹員A"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唔......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，快回去！", "name": "辦事處幹員B"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "fadetime": 0.5, "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶回來了！", "name": "辦事處幹員A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦了，接下來交給我就好。", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不確定這個孩子是不是感染者，他一直抱著這根法杖，應該是會點法術——還要我們再做點什麼嗎？", "name": "辦事處幹員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們先休息一下吧，我去給他做個檢查。辦事處裡留了幾個人守著消息，你們只要保證這裡不會被人發現就好。", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！我去弄點宵夜給你們墊墊肚子，這孩子看上去也沒怎麼吃飯，我準備點粥來。", "name": "辦事處幹員B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，那我先進去了。", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ri_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才十幾歲吧......這種年紀的孩子就受這種苦，唉。", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "體表無明顯礦石病病灶，但......根據檢測結果，已經是感染者了......", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傷口不算嚴重，但身體虛弱，用上源石技藝加速癒合......", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抑制劑還有儲備，鎮定劑已經注射。", "name": "醫療幹員"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_016_medic"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（發電機好吵，檢查也做完了，接下來用不上這些設備了，燈開著也太亮，不容易安睡。）", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（把燈給他關上，我再去把發電機關了，讓這個孩子睡個好覺吧。）", "name": "醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "char_016_medic"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snapping", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（定個時，過兩個小時再來看一下。)", "name": "醫療幹員"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉。", "name": "醫療幹員"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑暗的帳篷裡，小小的身影蜷縮在床上。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發燒和疲勞帶來的身體上的痛苦抵消了藥劑帶來的鎮靜作用，他在並不平和的夢中突然想去尋找些什麼。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是父母的懷抱，也許是家的溫暖。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些讓人感到幸福的事物在一天前已經離開他遠去，即使沒有清晰地意識到，現在在夢裡他仍舊為失去這些而感到痛苦。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......咳咳咳！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......好黑......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也沒有人......嗯......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......真的好黑，這裡也沒有電嗎？", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿、旁邊有什麼東西......輸液瓶？媽媽送我出來後......我、我被救了？", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#5$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周圍有什麼嗎......啊，我的法杖還在。", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#11$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，是兩個叔叔找到了我，是他們把我帶到這裡來了，我一定要謝謝他們......！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#11$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下床看看，呼......啊......坐起來都好累......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......誰都不在，只有我一個人。", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，媽媽怎麼什麼都不給我說，只讓我往外跑......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我和爸爸媽媽，還能再見嗎，嗚......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼黑又一個人都沒有，他們是不是遇到什麼事了......我、我會法術的，媽媽教過我......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虛弱的男孩倚躺在病床上，伸手去勾放在床邊的法杖。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "法杖是他自己一點一點拼出來的，破損的零件，廢棄的礦石，終於在某一天於他手中發出了光芒。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“光芒”，他想著這個詞。他想點起一團光，去幫助救了他的人。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor_u", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個玻璃燈罩居然沒有破損，還有這些齒輪和螺釘，明明都還很好，只是因為機器不能用了就被扔了，真可惜。", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過零件已經收集齊了！把這個線接到面板上面，再連到這裡......用下法術試試看？", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚哇，電到了！好痛......好難啊......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸媽媽還沒回家，一定要在他們回來前做好，他們一定會很高興的！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等以後找到好工作，我要給媽媽買很多藥，把她的病治好，爸爸也不用在工廠打工......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿......擰螺絲好費勁，爸爸的力氣真的很大，每次做什麼都能很快做好......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！一定要在他們回來前做好！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor_u", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽，你看！你教我的法術，我能用在這個法杖上了！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_m", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿——看，亮起來了！這個法杖也是我自己拼的！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#3$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽教我的法術我都記得，我都記在本子上了，增高電壓——嘿！快看！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#3$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_m", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我學得很快吧，我要做這裡最厲害的法術師，我要讓我們家有用不完的電，白天也可以開燈！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor_u", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$smallearthquake", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽，等下，他們都說出去了就會得病，你不要——", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是爸爸的工廠？爸爸還沒回來，爸爸在那裡？！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我去，媽媽讓我也去，我也會法術，我也能——", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#7$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在無數個夢裡，他勇猛地衝出被母親鎖上的家門，力大無窮地掀開工廠裡那些泛著光澤的廢渣，大人們嘴裡可怕的病對他沒有任何影響。"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他用母親教他的法術照亮了半片天空，人們在他的光下救治著一個又一個昏迷不醒的工人，他的爸爸只受了輕傷，也加入了救人的隊伍。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回家後，他們搬離了這裡，到了一個空氣裡不再飛著粉塵的地方。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他學會了更多的法術，和爸爸媽媽一起，一直幸福地生活著。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿——拿到了......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿——", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_m", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ri_1", "fadetime": 1.2, "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......只有一點點，只能照亮一點點......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是足夠了，能照亮腳下的路，就可以幫到別人了......！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#10$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冰冷的空氣湧入鼻腔，虛弱的佩洛男孩一直想做到像夢裡那樣的事。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工廠的廢墟前，他第一次見到媽媽使用了這麼大規模的法術，光芒湧入黑夜，照亮著廢墟裡的每一個角落。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他也想做出那種，能夠用自己的光幫助別人的事。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿、好冷——", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帳篷好大，這裡真的沒有人，他們、他們都去哪裡了？", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸說過，能幫到別人的時候一定要去幫，這樣、這樣我們才能生活得更好......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好黑，不會真的出事了吧......我、我要去——", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#5$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚、渾身都好酸......外面是哪裡？", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樹林？是、是山後面那片嗎......好遠啊......這片樹林媽媽給我說過，這裡、這裡很少有人來，很危險......", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#2$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼晚了，他們也沒有燈，肯定需要我幫忙，我、我要像媽媽那樣......幫到別人！", "name": "虛弱的佩洛男孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_253_greyy_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_253_greyy_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去外面找